        "TileImage": "$($repository 2af0e3d2-86d6-421a-95d8-5dacb67cae60).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon 47,\n\n\r\rThe diocese of which the coastal town of Sapienza is part of, recently discovered that three church workers pocketed a significant portion of funds for the clerical community. The trio allegedly used their earnings for &quot;lucrative pursuits&quot; - the kind of activities a devout collective is more likely to renounce. It is up to you to infiltrate the church as a priest and teach the trio a lesson.\n\n\r\rWe have a suit waiting for you in the church&#39;s basement.",
